# Compute · Mac + Hetzner only

Cloud Cursor agents **must not** use the cloud VM for heavy or long-running compute.

## Do not run on cloud agent VM

- `wrangler dev` / `npm run build` / `npm ci` in `coming-soon/`
- `graphify update` / `graphify query` (unless `graphify-out/` already exists from Mac)
- Aikido full scans, load tests, browser E2E loops
- SSH to Hetzner (`brmste-*` — Mac-only anyway)

## Cloud agent may run

- Git read/write, docs, small shell (git, gh metadata)
- **Read-only** MCP: `Cloudflare-bindings`, `Cloudflare-observability`, docs servers
- Point operator to Mac/Hetzner scripts when verification or deploy is needed

## Operator runs on THE KOHINOOR MAC

```bash
bash scripts/run-on-kohinoor-mac.sh help
bash scripts/run-on-kohinoor-mac.sh all
```

Hetzner fleet deploy: `bash scripts/deploy-md-render-hetzner.sh` (SSH from Mac).

Full policy: [docs/COMPUTE-MAC-HETZNER.md](../../docs/COMPUTE-MAC-HETZNER.md)
